  <description><![CDATA[<p>The 5 star Pullman Timi Ama is situated in a truly beautiful position with amazing uninterrupted sea views over the <strong>Bay of Villasimius</strong>. Between the hotel and the beach is a natural salt lagoon where pink flamingos are often to be seen. The beach itself is a few minutes stroll away, although a free buggy shuttle service operates throughout the day. Sunbeds are provided free of charge (except in the front two rows) and the <em>I Genepri</em> restaurant is open for lunch and à la carte dinner.</p>]]></description>
