  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The 5* Pullman Timi Ama is a stunning hotel, which offers uninterrupted sea views over the Bay of Villasimius. It is only a few minutes walk away from the beach and also a natural salt lagoon, where guests can often spot flamingos! The hotel has several lounges, bars and restaurants, as well as its own spa and wellness area.</p>]]></listingDescription>
